Failure mode: if MCP activation changes agent behavior unpredictably, leaks broader filesystem context, or makes transcript reproduction impossible, abandon it.

Recommendation: **no-go on hooks ŌåÆ mopsus; go with per-thread MCP activation ŌåÆ heated-debate**. Next action: define a single `shelley.ts` experimental flag for one debate-local read-only MCP, with no changes to mopsus.
